<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>上传说明</title>
        <style>
            :root {
                color-scheme: light;
                --bg: #f2eee7;
                --ink: #1f2933;
                --muted: #5f6b76;
                --panel: rgba(255, 250, 244, 0.82);
                --line: rgba(35, 48, 64, 0.1);
                --emerald: #0f766e;
                --emerald-soft: rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.12);
                --amber: #b45309;
                --amber-soft: rgba(180, 83, 9, 0.12);
                --shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(28, 35, 43, 0.12);
            }

            * {
                box-sizing: border-box;
            }

            body {
                margin: 0;
                min-height: 100vh;
                font-family: "PingFang SC", "Noto Serif SC", "Microsoft YaHei", serif;
                color: var(--ink);
                background:
                    radial-gradient(circle at 12% 18%, rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.18), transparent 22%),
                    radial-gradient(circle at 88% 12%, rgba(180, 83, 9, 0.18), transparent 18%),
                    linear-gradient(180deg, #f7f2ea 0%, #efe6d9 100%);
            }

            body::before {
                content: "";
                position: fixed;
                inset: 0;
                pointer-events: none;
                background-image:
                    linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18) 1px, transparent 1px),
                    linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18) 1px, transparent 1px);
                background-size: 28px 28px;
                mask-image: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), transparent 78%);
            }

            .wrap {
                width: min(1120px, calc(100% - 32px));
                margin: 0 auto;
                padding: 36px 0 56px;
            }

            .hero {
                position: relative;
                overflow: hidden;
                padding: 36px;
                border: 1px solid var(--line);
                border-radius: 32px;
                background:
                    linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.84), rgba(255, 248, 240, 0.74)),
                    rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
                box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            }

            .hero::after {
                content: "";
                position: absolute;
                right: -80px;
                top: -60px;
                width: 240px;
                height: 240px;
                border-radius: 50%;
                background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.18), transparent 66%);
            }

            .hero-grid {
                position: relative;
                display: grid;
                gap: 24px;
                grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.3fr) minmax(260px, 0.7fr);
                align-items: end;
            }

            .eyebrow {
                display: inline-flex;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 8px;
                margin: 0 0 14px;
                padding: 8px 14px;
                border-radius: 999px;
                background: var(--emerald-soft);
                color: var(--emerald);
                font-size: 12px;
                font-weight: 800;
                letter-spacing: 0.12em;
                text-transform: uppercase;
            }

            h1 {
                margin: 0;
                max-width: 9em;
                font-size: clamp(34px, 6vw, 64px);
                line-height: 0.98;
                letter-spacing: -0.04em;
            }

            .lead {
                margin: 18px 0 0;
                max-width: 720px;
                color: var(--muted);
                font-size: 17px;
                line-height: 1.8;
            }

            .hero-side {
                display: grid;
                gap: 14px;
            }

            .metric,
            .notice,
            .card {
                border: 1px solid var(--line);
                border-radius: 24px;
                background: var(--panel);
                box-shadow: var(--shadow);
                backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
            }

            .metric {
                padding: 20px 22px;
            }

            .metric-label {
                color: var(--muted);
                font-size: 13px;
                letter-spacing: 0.08em;
                text-transform: uppercase;
            }

            .metric-value {
                margin-top: 8px;
                font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 42px);
                font-weight: 800;
                line-height: 1;
            }

            .metric-note {
                margin-top: 10px;
                color: var(--muted);
                font-size: 14px;
                line-height: 1.6;
            }

            .notice {
                margin-top: 18px;
                padding: 16px 18px;
                background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(180, 83, 9, 0.12), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72));
                color: #8a4b12;
                font-size: 14px;
                line-height: 1.7;
            }

            .section-head {
                display: flex;
                align-items: end;
                justify-content: space-between;
                gap: 16px;
                margin: 28px 2px 16px;
            }

            .section-head h2 {
                margin: 0;
                font-size: 24px;
            }

            .section-head p {
                margin: 0;
                color: var(--muted);
                font-size: 14px;
            }

            .grid {
                display: grid;
                gap: 18px;
                grid-template-columns: repeat(12, minmax(0, 1fr));
            }

            .card {
                padding: 24px;
            }

            .card.wide {
                grid-column: span 7;
            }

            .card.tall {
                grid-column: span 5;
            }

            .card.full {
                grid-column: 1 / -1;
            }

            .tag {
                display: inline-flex;
                align-items: center;
                padding: 7px 12px;
                border-radius: 999px;
                background: var(--emerald-soft);
                color: var(--emerald);
                font-size: 12px;
                font-weight: 800;
                letter-spacing: 0.04em;
            }

            .card h3 {
                margin: 14px 0 12px;
                font-size: 24px;
                line-height: 1.2;
            }

            .card p {
                margin: 0;
                color: var(--muted);
                line-height: 1.8;
            }

            ol,
            ul {
                margin: 0;
                padding-left: 20px;
                color: var(--muted);
                line-height: 1.85;
            }

            li + li {
                margin-top: 8px;
            }

            .tips {
                display: grid;
                gap: 12px;
                margin-top: 18px;
            }

            .tip {
                display: flex;
                gap: 12px;
                align-items: start;
                padding: 14px 16px;
                border-radius: 18px;
                background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
                border: 1px solid rgba(31, 41, 51, 0.08);
            }

            .tip-index {
                flex: none;
                width: 30px;
                height: 30px;
                display: grid;
                place-items: center;
                border-radius: 50%;
                background: var(--emerald-soft);
                color: var(--emerald);
                font-weight: 800;
                font-size: 14px;
            }

            .tip strong {
                display: block;
                margin-bottom: 4px;
                font-size: 15px;
            }

            .table {
                display: grid;
                gap: 12px;
                margin-top: 16px;
            }

            .row {
                display: grid;
                grid-template-columns: 180px 1fr;
                gap: 14px;
                padding: 16px 18px;
                border-radius: 18px;
                background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.76);
                border: 1px solid rgba(31, 41, 51, 0.08);
            }

            .row strong {
                font-size: 15px;
            }

            .row span {
                color: var(--muted);
                line-height: 1.7;
            }

            .footer-note {
                margin-top: 18px;
                padding-top: 14px;
                border-top: 1px dashed rgba(31, 41, 51, 0.14);
                color: var(--muted);
                font-size: 14px;
                line-height: 1.7;
            }

            @media (max-width: 860px) {
                .hero {
                    padding: 24px;
                    border-radius: 26px;
                }

                .hero-grid,
                .grid {
                    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                }

                .card.wide,
                .card.tall,
                .card.full {
                    grid-column: auto;
                }
            }

            @media (max-width: 560px) {
                .wrap {
                    width: min(100% - 20px, 1120px);
                    padding: 20px 0 36px;
                }

                .hero,
                .card,
                .metric,
                .notice {
                    border-radius: 20px;
                }

                .hero,
                .card {
                    padding: 18px;
                }

                .row {
                    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                    gap: 8px;
                }
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <main class="wrap">
            <section class="hero">
                <div class="hero-grid">
                    <div>
                        <p class="eyebrow">Upload Guide</p>
                        <h1>文件上传说明</h1>
                        <p class="lead">
                            这份说明页用于帮助你快速准备可上传文件。当前版本更适合演示型内容，建议优先使用小体积文本、截图、图标或单页 PDF 做验证。
                        </p>
                        <div class="notice">
                            上传前先确认文件大小小于 <strong>65536 字节</strong>。超过当前限制时，系统不会接收文件内容，看起来就会像“上传无响应”。
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <aside class="hero-side">
                        <div class="metric">
                            <div class="metric-label">当前上限</div>
                            <div class="metric-value">64 KB</div>
                            <div class="metric-note">适合测试文本、小图、轻量说明页和一页式 PDF。</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="metric">
                            <div class="metric-label">推荐策略</div>
                            <div class="metric-value">先小后大</div>
                            <div class="metric-note">先用稳定的小文件确认链路正常，再逐步测试边界体积。</div>
                        </div>
                    </aside>
                </div>
            </section>

            <div class="section-head">
                <h2>上传前准备</h2>
                <p>按这个顺序检查，问题会少很多。</p>
            </div>

            <section class="grid">
                <article class="card wide">
                    <span class="tag">快速准备</span>
                    <h3>3 步准备一个稳定的测试文件</h3>
                    <div class="tips">
                        <div class="tip">
                            <div class="tip-index">1</div>
                            <div>
                                <strong>先用纯文本打底</strong>
                                <p>新建一个 `.txt` 文件，写几行内容保存。它最容易判断是链路问题还是文件格式问题。</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="tip">
                            <div class="tip-index">2</div>
                            <div>
                                <strong>再试小尺寸图片</strong>
                                <p>优先选图标、界面截图或压缩后的图片，不要一上来就传大照片。</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="tip">
                            <div class="tip-index">3</div>
                            <div>
                                <strong>最后试单页 PDF</strong>
                                <p>如果文本和图片都正常，再用一页以内的 PDF 检查文档上传路径。</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>

                <article class="card tall">
                    <span class="tag">大小检查</span>
                    <h3>上传前一定看体积</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>在文件管理器中选中文件。</li>
                        <li>打开“属性”或“显示简介”。</li>
                        <li>确认文件小于 64 KB 后再上传。</li>
                        <li>如果接近上限，优先重新压缩再试。</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="footer-note">
                        这一步最容易省时间。很多“上传失败”本质上只是超过限制，不是服务异常。
                    </div>
                </article>

                <article class="card full">
                    <span class="tag">常见原因</span>
                    <h3>上传未完成，通常是这几类原因</h3>
                    <div class="table">
                        <div class="row">
                            <strong>文件太大</strong>
                            <span>当前版本限制 64 KB，超过时服务端不会按预期接收完整内容。</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row">
                            <strong>登录已过期</strong>
                            <span>页面停留过久后会话可能失效，上传请求会因为鉴权失败被拒绝。</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row">
                            <strong>网络中断</strong>
                            <span>请求提交过程中如果网络抖动，上传会在浏览器侧被中断。</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row">
                            <strong>浏览器中途取消</strong>
                            <span>切标签页、刷新页面或重复点击上传，都可能让当前请求提前结束。</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>

                <article class="card full">
                    <span class="tag">格式参考</span>
                    <h3>推荐优先测试的文件类型</h3>
                    <div class="table">
                        <div class="row">
                            <strong>text/plain</strong>
                            <span>适合说明文档、接口示例、配置片段和最基础的链路验证。</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row">
                            <strong>image/png</strong>
                            <span>适合图标、透明背景图片和界面截图，体积通常更可控。</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row">
                            <strong>image/jpeg</strong>
                            <span>适合压缩后的照片或较轻量的展示图，注意原图通常偏大。</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row">
                            <strong>application/pdf</strong>
                            <span>适合单页说明、样张和合同预览，不建议直接上传多页大文件。</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="footer-note">
                        如果只是验证功能是否可用，优先从 `text/plain` 和小型 `PNG` 开始，定位问题最快。
                    </div>
                </article>
            </section>
        </main>
    </body>
</html>
